attributes.title: A mockery
attributes.review: Even though I cannot legally vote until 2024 I am very disappointed with the loading screen :(((. (my eyes have been scarred from now on). The audacity you have to tell me to take a survey on YouTube videos and give you money is completely outrageous. Wanting to take money from children. You should be ashamed of yourself.  Once a I opened the app I felt a rush to my head like I was going to vomit. Absolutely disgusting and vile of all of you.
